Vite is faster front end library
1. npm create vite@latest
Project name: fitness-app
Framework: React
TypeScript

2. cd my app
3. npm i
4. npm run dev

5. Animation library, npm i framer-motion
6. npm i react-anchor-link-smooth-scroll@1.0.12
6. Icons made by Tailwind npm i @heroicons/react

Dev dependencies
7. npm i -D @types/react-anchor-link-smooth-scroll@1.0.2 @types/node
8. Installing tailwind for Vite: npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
9. npx tailwindcss init -p
10. npm i -D prettier prettier-plugin-tailwindcss